</li></ul><div class="para" label-module="para">妖精、马人、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%8B%BC%E4%BA%BA">狼人</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%9C%E9%AA%90">夜骐</a>、人鱼、凤凰、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%8B%AC%E8%A7%92%E5%85%BD">独角兽</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%BB%E5%B0%8F%E7%B2%BE%E7%81%B5">家养小精灵</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%91%84%E9%AD%82%E6%80%AA">摄魂怪</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E8%84%8A%E8%83%8C%E9%BE%99">挪威脊背龙</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%81%AB%E7%90%83%E9%BE%99">中国火球龙</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8%E7%9F%AD%E9%BC%BB%E9%BE%99">瑞典短鼻龙</a>、匈牙利树蜂龙、威尔士绿龙、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%B9%B0%E5%A4%B4%E9%A9%AC%E8%BA%AB%E6%9C%89%E7%BF%BC%E5%85%BD">鹰头马身有翼兽</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%81%AB%E8%9E%83%E8%9F%B9">火螃蟹</a>、人头狮身龙尾兽、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%82%B8%E5%B0%BE%E8%9E%BA">炸尾螺</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BC%97%E6%B4%9B%E4%BC%AF%E6%AF%9B%E8%99%AB">弗洛伯毛虫</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%9F%B3">打人柳</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9B%BC%E5%BE%B7%E6%8B%89%E8%8D%89">曼德拉草</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AA%9A%E5%A8%83">媚娃</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%A3%9F%E5%B0%B8%E9%AC%BC">食尸鬼</a>、爱尔兰小矮妖、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%9C%B0%E7%B2%BE">地精</a></div>
